{"tid":1786070,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(想推老婆做總統?)奧巴馬：女主政優於男 老男戀棧權位是問題根源","createTime":"2019-12-17T01:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T02:11:01.000Z","uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e5c50fbd93a8ce6c2fd001aa5f718220cf05ebb5","tid":1786070,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T01:16:03.000Z","msg":"美國前總統奧巴馬周一表示，如果世界各國都由女性治理，那麼人民生活水準和管治效果將有全面改善。同時他認為，佔據權位的年長男性是多數問題的根源。<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬偕同夫人米歇爾一同出席新加坡成長學院的活動，談到領導才能。他說，他在總統任內就曾深思，這個世界若由女性治理會有何結果。他認為，女性雖非完美，但「無疑優於」男性。<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬指出，世界上多數問題都出於戀棧權位的年長者，其中又以男性為主，「看看這個世界，想想問題，」。<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬進一步表示：「對政治領導人而言，重要的是設法提醒自己，人在其位是為了要做事，而不是要過一輩子，或滿足自大心理和權力慾。」<br />\n<br />\n現任美國總統特朗普以70歲之齡就任總統，是美國史上上任時年齡最大的總統。在中國，66歲的國家主席習近平，在去年3月全國兩會通過修憲後，為他本人終身執政鋪平了道路。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191217/60385715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191217%2F60385715&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0mVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=6637fa08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191217%2F60385715&h=4050a062\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191217/60385715</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻煩經常在於老男人不願讓賢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />試問默克爾做左總理幾多年?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"451b7ffa7cbddea2bc0841fa3bebff4b199fd179","tid":1786070,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T01:18:08.000Z","msg":"你老味歧視老年男人？<br />\n哩啲又唔講平權嗱？"},{"pid":"d13df6e19d4ac80202dd55eb987f5a66f0375602","tid":1786070,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T01:23:07.000Z","msg":"我諗問題係老而唔係男"},{"pid":"2f75b962fd743f51215ba35537c744c3f06b2832","tid":1786070,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T01:36:26.000Z","msg":"望下林鄭未知啱定唔啱囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf80a7a7d0262eef59c19117595f7a87d9141a8","tid":1786070,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T01:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港<br />\n搵ai黎做領導人未得 將所以問題數據化"},{"pid":"db507cb9e6268f7a5293a337fa40aa6cf22ea32e","tid":1786070,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T01:52:29.000Z","msg":"林鄭 昂山 默克爾 ：<br />\n<br />\n我諗問題都係年紀大"},{"pid":"91f217aa5c32bb651fdc335abcb1d83b52971bb6","tid":1786070,"uid":41317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T02:11:01.000Z","msg":"關男女咩事<br />\n問題係老人戀棧權位唔俾後生上做成施政代溝"}]}